Sheep pox and goat pox, Kazakhstan
----------------------------------
Information received on (and dated) 25 Sep 2013 from Dr Mereke Taitubayev, Chairman, Committee of veterinary control and supervision, Ministry of Agriculture, Astana, Kazakhstan

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 20 Aug 2013
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 23 Aug 2013
Report date: 25 Sep 2013
Date submitted to OIE: 25 Sep 2013
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Capripoxvirus_ (family _Poxviridae_)
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks (1)
