Total outbreaks: 1
Outbreak 1: private courtyard, Konaeyv, Shussky [Shuskiy], Dzhambul [Jambyl]
Date of start of the outbreak: 20 Aug 2013
Outbreak status: resolved (17 Sep 2013)
Epidemiological unit: farm
